type: bugfix
subject: Updated drakxtools package fixes several issues
src:
  2:
   core:
     - drakxtools-14.22.4-1.1.mga2
description: |
  - diskdrake offers to resize NTFS again
  - drakboot fixes removing LVM entries when saving /etc/fstab (mga#5811)
  - drakclock fixes crashing if timezones cannot be listed (mga#6787)
  Last but not least, it fixes a rare crash when a banner icon doesn't exist (mga#5223)
references:
 - https://bugs.mageia.org/show_bug.cgi?id=9741
